Architecture change
Extracted run_trading_cycle() → core/cycle_runner.py
Introduced CycleSnapshot dataclass — single object carrying all UI state per cycle
Background trading worker runs cycles; UI updates from snapshots
New modules: core/, ui/dashboard_app.py, ui/formatters.py, ui/plain_dashboard.py, ui/timeline.py

Priority 2: Agent Interaction Layer
Operator control without editing config files or restarting.

Runtime controller (agent/runtime_controller.py)
Persists flags to logs/runtime.json:

Global pause / resume
pause stocks / pause crypto (asset-class scoped)
force_hold — block new trades
risk reduced — position size multiplier
All operator actions logged to events.jsonl
Runtime flags are checked before AI execution in the cycle runner — trading core stays unchanged.

Command registry (agent/commands.py + agent/validator.py)
TUI command bar supports:

