New modules: agent/

Priority 3: AI Memory & Reflection
Stateless PicoClaw calls became context-aware via deterministic reflection (no extra AI call for memory).

Memory store (memory/reflection.py)
Writes compressed logs/memory.json after each cycle:

ai_mood — healthy / cautious / rate_limited / etc.
market_bias — bullish / bearish / neutral / cautious
confidence_bias, recent_win_rate
best_recent_symbol, worst_recent_symbol
Rolling last_decisions, lessons, mistakes
Reflection rules derive from: cycle outcomes, day P&L, AI failure rate in recent events, rejection patterns.

Prompt injection
ai/prompt_builder.py injects a MEMORY block into every PicoClaw prompt so the AI sees recent behavior without full history bloat.

Dashboard integration
AI panel shows mood, bias, and latest lesson alongside the current decision.

New modules: memory/

