Pipeline Architecture (End of Day 1)
UNIVERSE (~120 stocks + ~40 crypto)
        ↓  batch bars (5d), scored
RADAR PROMOTE (top N movers)
        ↓  batch bars (30d), full indicators
DEEP SHORTLIST (≤ MAX_DEEP_SCAN, default 20)
        ↓  strategy signals + compressed prompt (AI_DETAIL_TOP_N full detail)
PICOCLAW AI DECISION
        ↓  parse JSON
RISK ENGINE (hard limits, cooldowns, runtime flags)
        ↓
EXECUTOR (Alpaca paper)
        ↓
LOGS + MEMORY REFLECTION + CycleSnapshot → Textual TUI
Design principle established on Day 1: Radar does the math at scale; AI only sees a narrow, ranked shortlist. Never feed 200 symbols to the model.

What Was Running by End of Day 1
